      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am honestly so sad to see this beauty go, but it is time for someone else to enjoy the ride! This car is in absolute pristine condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I have babied it since day one, always kept it tucked away in the garage, and it is still sparkling inside and out. It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for its next big adventure. You really have to see it in person to believe how well it's been kept. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
