    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade AP1 S2000 featuring the high-compression F20C inline-four. This naturally aspirated masterpiece achieves a 9,000 RPM redline, delivering power through a longitudinal 6-speed close-ratio manual transmission to a Torsen limited-slip differential. The chassis integrity is absolute, utilizing the original X-bone frame and a four-wheel double-wishbone suspension setup that remains factory-spec tight. This specimen retains all original VIN-matching body panels with flawless paint depth and a pristine interior free of bolster wear. Mechanically synchronized and aesthetically untouched, it represents the pinnacle of analog driver engagement.",
      "price": 48500.0,
